

File name should always start with test
Function name aur method name should also start with test_
class name should start with Test
when we follow these rules pytest will recognize these files , functions and classes following the rules so
without giving function call we can execute the test function and without creating an object we can execute
a test function ,and without creating an object we can test the test class.

-v stands for verbosity it gives the detail description of the code
-s stands for scripting and print all the print statement
Pytest cannot recognize the function that aren't inside these rules.
In case of test classes we need not create objects and call the functions. If we do so the execution will happen
twice
